{"tid":2105141,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權紀錄】 反送中一周年 全程戰線記錄","createTime":"2020-07-12T12:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T07:12:52.000Z","uid":361535,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b14ea54e5a0642463862feafccd04e628f84b45a","tid":2105141,"uid":361535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=El9Oxlmt2jo&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEl9Oxlmt2jo%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=5388de93\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=El9Oxlmt2jo&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n從6.12到6.12，香港人經歷咗<span class=\"gold\"><strong>365日嘅抗爭</strong></span>。希望藉住呢個機會用<strong><span class=\"gold\">戰線地圖</span></strong>嘅形式去紀錄呢一年香港人嘅血與淚，所以特登整咗個戰線紀錄短片俾大家回顧我哋一齊行過嘅路，同埋一啲紀錄抗爭者吶喊嘅地圖同數字。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，撐住！"},{"pid":"426e4096e982a210933988729015359c5bf1eac9","tid":2105141,"uid":361535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:26:02.000Z","msg":"【回顧一．夜幕降臨】<br />\n<br />\n［0:00 - 4:50］<br />\n<br />\n第一部份的回顧由政府提交《逃犯條例》修訂草案開始，到特首林鄭月娥宣佈「撤回」。在面對這條「惡法」，香港人沒有坐以待斃，更衍生出各式各樣表達我們訴求的方式，例如：流水式集會、人鏈、連儂牆等。<br />\n<br />\n未來在「國安法」的陰霾下，香港人自由的空間進一步收窄。讓我們在回顧中發現我們曾以創業建立了不少的抗爭模式，相信未來的我們也能在絕望中找出一條屬於香港人的光明之路。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油。"},{"pid":"7f12c8a42e45d796567686a67a848de24b3f52d6","tid":2105141,"uid":74412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"好有心思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111bb1461f69efc57944c14d4552e53b4b78e9cd","tid":2105141,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0a5cb6038f7cdcd8992da1120f14e8a0619aa8","tid":2105141,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:40:51.000Z","msg":"好PRO<br />\n戰爭地圖咁<br />\n希望大家記住慘痛既一年 記得逝去既手足 唔好放棄"},{"pid":"fbc377c45ac95800c52ff315177e625564c71426","tid":2105141,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:48:03.000Z","msg":"好撚高質 睇到喊..."},{"pid":"104fed12aadb545dd2e8b01a8f39938cfb53fa44","tid":2105141,"uid":66331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"從6.12到6.12，香港人經歷咗<span class=\"red\">365日</span>嘅抗爭。希望藉住呢個機會用戰線地圖嘅形式去紀錄呢一年香港人嘅血與淚，所以特登整咗個戰線紀錄短片俾大家回顧我哋一齊行過嘅路，同埋一啲紀錄抗爭者吶喊嘅地圖同數字。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月有29日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20989dcc7d1c12656d0ee2e43f610ee7db4e1a3e","tid":2105141,"uid":361535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"104fed12aadb545dd2e8b01a8f39938cfb53fa44","tid":2105141,"uid":66331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:48:31.000Z","msg":"從6.12到6.12，香港人經歷咗<span class=\"red\">365日</span>嘅抗爭。希望藉住呢個機會用戰線地圖嘅形式去紀錄呢一年香港人嘅血與淚，所以特登整咗個戰線紀錄短片俾大家回顧我哋一齊行過嘅路，同埋一啲紀錄抗爭者吶喊嘅地圖同數字。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月有29日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b93addc2ab8431257024a2fa5b26d517085dd2","tid":2105141,"uid":361535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"【回顧二｜衝突升級】<br />\n<br />\n  [4:50 - 8:23]<br />\n<br />\n第二部份回顧由特首林鄭月娥宣佈「撤回」條例，到民主派區選大敗建制派。雖然政府撤回了送中條例，但卻拒絕回應香港人其餘訴求，並不斷將警暴升級，甚至推出禁蒙面法阻止市民實踐公民權利。因此，抗爭者只能「以勇制暴」，使用更激進的手段表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n這段時間的傷亡、被捕、催淚彈等數字屢創新高，其間更直接導致至少2人死亡。當我們被「國安法」白色恐怖籠罩的同時，勿忘過去為香港犧牲的手足，為他們繼續走下這條自由之路。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗。"},{"pid":"da83f90b06ab8ed84b7aaea040498ad396521ad2","tid":2105141,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T14:58:32.000Z","msg":"高質<br />\n推"},{"pid":"39cf3fd09afac95de72dbf9c9f1795747113ce2c","tid":2105141,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:05:36.000Z","msg":"咁高質都無人推?"},{"pid":"0c3902ba5e1765f7073fe411fc3e8a1dcbd3fc4e","tid":2105141,"uid":41512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648846ec9d92cb209b52ef4030749312ae7b2836","tid":2105141,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q6pHdTJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ6pHdTJ.gif&h=26da3e82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25b627fcba53a7a4204b192c1a63354330e10a17","tid":2105141,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"點解圍城燒狗屋呢d增加士氣既野唔放落去"},{"pid":"059bc30dd42ffb986c5ca29aa5d298d6f6ae4b5f","tid":2105141,"uid":361535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:12:52.000Z","msg":"【回顧三｜疫下抗爭】<br />\n<br />\n［8:23 - 15-01］<br />\n<br />\n第三部份由民主派區選大敗建制派，到反送中大規模爆發一周年。經歷理大圍城一役，運動開始降溫。尤其是在一月尾武漢肺炎爆發後，運動被疫情、限聚令等窒礙。然而，抗爭者憑著無限創意，將戰線移至網絡，繼續提醒香港人毋忘初衷。<br />\n<br />\n然而，中國政府從未想過放過香港人，急於推出「國安法」，意圖噤聲香港。在回顧抗爭一周年之際，我們亦要思索未來的去向。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，撐住。"}]}